name: VOXELFINE #2: "Saturn Devouring His Son" by Francisco Goya 3D voxelart model (.glb)
description: The original pixel art for this piece was my first pixel rendition of fine art. This is also my favorite painting by my favorite European painter. Voxelfines are collectible 3D voxel models of iconic works of art. They are ready to be imported into a VR or AR experience of your choice. By Lorem Ipsum, 2021.
